  <brief_title>Evaluation of a Mandibular Advancement Device in the Treatment of Obstructive Sleep Apnea Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Evaluation of Mandibular Advancement by Herbst Device in the Treatment of Moderate Obstructive Sleep Apnea Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
